# Session Init Protocol

**Wajib dibaca AI agent saat mulai session baru di project {{PROJECT_NAME}}.**

---

## Step 1: Read Environment

- Read `.agent/context/environment.json`
- Detect `active_profile` (windows/linux) dan `techStack` versions

## Step 2: Read Project Context

- Read `.agent/context/project-context.json`
- Catat `workspace_root`, `is_multi_project_root`, `subprojects` list, `default_preset`

## Step 3: Read AGENTS.md SSOT

- Read root `AGENTS.md` (file ini adalah SSOT multi-tool)
- Catat: Prinsip Multi-Project, Urutan Prioritas, Tech Stack, active Gotchas

## Step 4: Index Memory

- Read `.agent/memory/index.json`
- Ringkas entries terbaru per kategori (last 5 per category jika tersedia)

## Step 5: Confirm Scope dengan User

- User sebutkan task scope: single file / module / full project
- AI konfirmasi scope sebelum eksekusi
- Jika scope tidak jelas: tanya, jangan assume

## Step 6: End-of-Session Protocol

- Jika ada lesson learned baru: buat file di `.agent/memory/entries/<category>/<date>-<topic>.md`
- Format nama file: `YYYY-MM-DD-topik-singkat.md`
- Update `.agent/memory/index.json`: tambah entry, update `last_updated`
- Jika entry layak di-share ke workspace root: gunakan `/memory-promote` skill

